==Introduction==

Welcome to [[How to Pass a Course]], a wikibook made for students. It covers subjects such as classroom seating, note taking, assignment completion, study techniques, to cramming techniques. It is our hope that students in both college and high school will be able to use this text throughout their years of education.

{{How to Pass a Course}}

